    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "SKYWAY WING ROOM, SAN FRANCISCO INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT, CALIFORNIA",
      "Patrons may observe the activities at the\nramps and\nrunways\nin utmost comfort,\nwhile enjoying the delicious dinners served\nin the beautiful glass-enclosed SKYWAY\nWING ROOM.\nDear Mrs. Hurdle,\nWe are very sorry\nbut matches are not to\nbe sent thru the mails.\nCo.,\nIf you think of some way\nto send them, or if you\nare up this\nway some-\nHoward\ntime, we would be very\nSt.,\nhappy to give you a box\nSan\nof our matches.\nFrancisco\nSincerely:\nSkyway Cafe\nE-9721\nUNITED\nSTATES\nPOSTATE\nCENT\nPOST CARD\nMrse\n161Q\nWashi\nStree\nS. E.\nDoC.\n2001.013.022"
    ],
